## SpringBoot和Mybatis

* 本次采用的是Java1.8版本
* 数据库采用的是MySQL，版本为5.7
* maven为3.6.1版本
* 数据库连接池使用的是阿里的Druid连接池
* SpringBoot版本为2.4.1
* 开发软件为IDEA2020



### 1 搭建环境

#### 1.3 配置环境

* 在pom.xml中添加依赖

```xml
        <dependency>
            <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
            <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-jdbc</artifactId>
        </dependency>
        <!--连接MySQL-->
        <!-- 我自己指定了MySQL连接驱动的版本为5.1.47 -->
        <dependency>
            <groupId>mysql</groupId>
            <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
            <version>5.1.47</version>
        </dependency>
        <!--   springboot连接mybatis     -->
        <dependency>
            <groupId>org.mybatis.spring.boot</groupId>
            <artifactId>mybatis-spring-boot-starter</artifactId>
            <version>1.3.2</version>
        </dependency>
        <dependency>
            <groupId>junit</groupId>
            <artifactId>junit</artifactId>
            <version>4.12</version>
        </dependency>
```

* 创建包结构

```xml
创建结构如下
--src
	--main
		--java
			--pojo
			--mapper
			XxxApplication.java
		--resources
			--mybatis
				--mapper
			--application.yml
	--test
		--java
--pom.xml
```

* 配置application.yml

```yaml
spring:
  datasource:
    username: root
    password: root
    url: jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/test?characterEncoding=utf8&useSSL=false
    driver-class-name: com.mysql.jdbc.Driver


mybatis:
  configuration:
    map-underscore-to-camel-case: true
  mapper-locations: classpath:mybatis/mapper/*.xml
  type-aliases-package: com.lyb.two.pojo

```

* 在主程序入口添加一个mapper扫描

```java

import org.mybatis.spring.annotation.MapperScan;
import org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;
import org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.SpringBootApplication;

//改成自己对应的包
@MapperScan("com.lyb.two.mapper")
@SpringBootApplication
public class TwoApplication {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        SpringApplication.run(TwoApplication.class, args);
    }

}
```

### 2 搭建项目

#### 2.1 创建实体类和Mapper

* 创建实体类student，对应数据库

```java
//添加get和set方法，无参有参构造，ToString方法
public class Student {
    private int id;
    private String name;
    private String classes;
    private String subject;
    private String score;
}
```

* 创建Mapper和对应的xml文件

```java
public interface StudentMapper {

    Student getStudentByid(Integer id);

    List<Student> QueryAllStudent();

    int deleteStudentById(Integer id);

    int insertStudent(Student student);

    int updateStudent(Student student);

}

```

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE mapper
        PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN"
        "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd">
<mapper namespace="com.lyb.two.mapper.StudentMapper">

    <!--    Student getStudentByid(int id);-->

    <!--    List<Student> QueryAllStudent();-->

    <!--    int deleteStudentById(Integer id);-->

    <!--    int insertStudent(Student student);-->

    <!--    int updateStudent(Student student);-->

</mapper>
```



#### 2.2 创建测试类

* 在接口处，右键，选择GO TO -- Test

![](data:image/png;base64,)

* 选择 Junit 4 ，在选择需要测试的接口

![](data:image/png;base64,)



#### 2.3 编写SQL语句

```xml
    <!--    Student getStudentByid(int id);-->
    <select id="getStudentByid" parameterType="int" resultType="student">
        select `id`,`name`,`classes`,`subject`,`score` from student where `id` = #{id}
    </select>

    <!--    List<Student> QueryAllStudent();-->
    <select id="QueryAllStudent" resultMap="studentmap">
        select * from student 
    </select>
    <resultMap id="studentmap" type="student">
        <result property="id" column="id" />
        <result property="name" column="name" />
        <result property="classes" column="classes" />
        <result property="subject" column="subject" />
        <result property="score" column="score" />
    </resultMap>

    <!--    int deleteStudentById(Integer id);-->
    <delete id="deleteStudentById" parameterType="int">
        delete from `student` where `id` = #{id}
    </delete>

    <!--    int insertStudent(Student student);-->
    <insert id="insertStudent" parameterType="student">
        insert into `student`(`name`,`classes`,`subject`,`score`)
                values (#{name},#{classes},#{subject},#{score})
    </insert>

    <!--    int updateStudent(Student student);-->
    <update id="updateStudent" parameterType="student">
        update `student` set `name` = #{name}, `classes` = #{classes},
                `subject` = #{subject}, `score` = #{score} where `id` = #{id}
    </update>

```
